('California AI Safety Bill Active', 'California AI safety bill went into effect January 2026, with OpenAI and Anthropic showing split positions on meaningful AI regulation legislation.', 'ai_policy', '{"jurisdiction": "California", "legislation": "AI safety bill", "status": "active", "effective": "January 2026", "company_positions": "split"}'),
