('Majorana Qubit Breakthrough', 'Researchers successfully read Majorana qubit states using quantum capacitance technique, advancing stable topological quantum computing where information spreads across linked quantum states resistant to noise.', 'quantum_computing', '{"breakthrough": "Majorana qubit readout", "technique": "quantum_capacitance", "advantage": "noise_resistance", "type": "topological_qubit"}'),
